{"tid":2165582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰高中生加入抗爭 舉白紙反獨裁","createTime":"2020-08-20T02:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T02:17:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"208f68f18c3b8c44bece4b551ebeff67fc05c9e0","tid":2165582,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T02:17:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200820/TYJSJSLS6JDMBBEPZNO37MQCIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200820%2FTYJSJSLS6JDMBBEPZNO37MQCIE%2F&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=6147fe46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200820%2FTYJSJSLS6JDMBBEPZNO37MQCIE%2F&h=1f9ec52d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200820/TYJSJSLS6JDMBBEPZNO37MQCIE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n泰高中生加入抗爭 舉白紙反獨裁<br />\n<br />\n泰國反政府示威持續，學生繼續在校園抗爭，除了大學生，亦有高中生加入。而警方昨以涉嫌違反內部安全、防疫措施及電腦罪行等，對六名示威者發出拘捕令，包括公開宣讀要求王室改革宣言的學生領袖。<br />\n<br />\n約2,000名曼谷郊區佛統府瑪希敦大學學生，前晚在校園足球場集會，聲援批評政府的講者，另外有人排隊聯署，要求修改軍方控制的憲法。至於同日較早時有30名曼谷高中生示威，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n高中生近日響應反政府活動，社交網站流傳照片和影片所見，多個城市的高中生，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cm1_BG1qTuLEpGy-SMW0CXB8_v0=/1413x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/STSKKST2HZDOZE2Q46HXY2TR4I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fcm1_BG1qTuLEpGy-SMW0CXB8_v0%3D%2F1413x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSTSKKST2HZDOZE2Q46HXY2TR4I.jpg&h=e4e7a830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■泰國學生舉起白紙示威。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警通緝六示威者<br />\n<br />\n另方面，逾3,000名示威者上周一在國立法政大學集會，警方昨向六名參與者發拘捕令，指他們可到警署自首，但不得帶民眾到場聲。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/美聯社"}]}